      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OUR REGARDS (4) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Binnaway Warrior (22.70) in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Top chance in this line up. LONG GULLY ASH (7) started big odds over 400m at this track (22.94) in Invitation but ran very well to fill a minor placing. Was a winner this track in lesser company the start prior. Solid record here at the distance winning nine races. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can feature again. URANA JAM DONUT (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 23.22 beating He's No Diva. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. OUR IVIE ROSE (5) placed last time and is worth some thought.",
